Package: metaphlanr
Title: Post-process MetaPhlAn2 output in R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Michael", "McLaren", email = "m.mclaren42@gmail.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides functions for working with MetaPhlAn2
    "clade_profiles" output in R, in order to perform community composition
    analyses that require read counts rather than MetaPhlAn2's standard output
    of relative abundances.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    magrittr,
    phyloseq,
    tidyverse
